Ena: (He works individually with each of his students, right? Sketches, oil paintings, everything...)
Ena: ...
Ena: (Each year many of his students get accepted because they took this course.)
Ena: (If I'm serious about getting into art school, then I should take this opportunity to get him to teach me one-on-one.)
